WEBVTT

00:01.080 --> 00:01.720
Your son wouldn't dare

00:02.720 --> 00:03.840
I fear the Chen family is too powerful

00:04.240 --> 00:05.680
Once any news leaks out

00:05.800 --> 00:07.200
They will immediately cover up the truth

00:07.800 --> 00:08.960
From local to court

00:09.320 --> 00:10.040
Every checkpoint

00:10.040 --> 00:11.000
They can reach

00:11.400 --> 00:12.640
Even I, a prince

00:12.960 --> 00:14.320
Am constantly in danger

00:14.720 --> 00:15.320
This time

00:16.240 --> 00:17.360
Whether I resist arrest

00:18.000 --> 00:18.800
Rashly confess

00:19.600 --> 00:21.160
Or elder brother is incited by the Chen family

00:21.680 --> 00:23.160
Even without Mother's care

00:23.560 --> 00:25.000
I might not see Father

00:26.080 --> 00:27.200
Facing such a Chen family

00:27.680 --> 00:29.080
Your son could only take risks

00:30.840 --> 00:31.680
Good

00:32.320 --> 00:34.000
Prince of Jin is very bold

00:34.640 --> 00:36.040
Getting a piece of hearsay

00:36.200 --> 00:37.600
Dares to take risks

00:37.720 --> 00:39.120
And deploy the city defense troops

00:39.600 --> 00:40.360
If one day

00:40.360 --> 00:41.080
You get news

00:41.080 --> 00:42.680
That I want to kill you

00:43.320 --> 00:45.400
Would you also dare to take risks

00:45.520 --> 00:46.720
And bind me?

00:47.200 --> 00:48.160
Your son absolutely wouldn't dare

00:51.200 --> 00:51.840
Enough

00:54.120 --> 00:55.960
If I drive you to death

00:57.240 --> 00:59.600
I'll only have one son left
